  demand (unlikely).</p>
  <p> This was written with the Ruby on Rails development framework. I picked it up for the purposes of this project, so when things break, it's likely
  they won't be handled elegantly. API rate limiting has NOT been implemented. I don't really know how to do it. Try not to spam requests
    and prevent others from doing anything. Bear with me!</p>
  <p>Special thanks to the people behind <a href="https://github.com/PeterBorah/vigor">Vigor</a> for their awesome Ruby wrapper for the API. It's
  really great stuff, and I would have a lot more trouble if it weren't for their great open-source organization and documentation.</p>
